{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/posts/icxgxa","result":{"data":{"sitePage":null},"pageContext":{"url":"posts/icxgxa","relativePath":"posts/icxgxa","frontmatter":{"title":"知乎“官方”机器人账号观察","stackbit_url_path":"posts/icxgxa","date":"2022-11-04T08:39:50","excerpt":"","tags":[],"categories":[],"template":"post"},"html":"<p>从 11 月份开始，我注意到自己的知乎账号，每天从下午 3 点开始，到深夜，不停有人在“关注”我，导致自己的关注者数量飙升。本来攒到的 800 多个关注者，花了一年多的时间，而最近 3 天一下子来了 1000 多名“关注者”，匪夷所思。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/221736/1667550017096-41ef032a-2abc-4466-be7e-87755d7a69aa.png#clientId=u3a2c44d1-d614-4&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=1&#x26;crop=1&#x26;from=paste&#x26;height=556&#x26;id=u9f94a078&#x26;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&#x26;name=image.png&#x26;originHeight=1112&#x26;originWidth=2116&#x26;originalType=binary%E2%88%B6=1&#x26;rotation=0&#x26;showTitle=false&#x26;size=132863&#x26;status=done&#x26;style=none&#x26;taskId=u312e2824-c2dd-4e0a-9d9c-38e02c605a4&#x26;title=&#x26;width=1058\" alt=\"image.png\"></p>\n<p>我随便点开了几个，立即知道其实他们不是真的人，而是机器人账号无疑了。只是以前，如果有机器人账号关注我，我点进去时，会显示被知乎反欺诈中心屏蔽。而那种机器人一般其实肉眼看不出，因为他们还有一些创作，点赞以及交互等等行为。而最近这几天的机器人账号，一看就是假的，不知道为什么反而没有被知乎反欺诈中心拦截？难道，他们其实就是知乎“官方”制造的机器人账号？我没有证据……</p>\n<p><a name=YowE9></a></p>\n<h1>爱用刘看山做为头像</h1>\n<p>虽然，对刘看山做了一些调色，但很明显还是刘看山。这是我怀疑它们来自“官方”的原因之一（主要原因是他们没有被拦截）。<br /><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/221736/1667550434242-5cbca63f-be44-4db3-aea9-cf030c8e2923.png#clientId=u3a2c44d1-d614-4&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=1&#x26;crop=1&#x26;from=paste&#x26;height=1040&#x26;id=u1c5f7588&#x26;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&#x26;name=IMG_7463.png&#x26;originHeight=2079&#x26;originWidth=960&#x26;originalType=binary%E2%88%B6=1&#x26;rotation=0&#x26;showTitle=false&#x26;size=672486&#x26;status=done&#x26;style=none&#x26;taskId=u83eb6f0b-9980-462f-9671-e9adf0c602d&#x26;title=&#x26;width=480\" alt=\"IMG_7463.png\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/221736/1667550461367-2b63a933-3e11-4536-bce0-aa12e6c17441.png#clientId=u3a2c44d1-d614-4&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=1&#x26;crop=1&#x26;from=paste&#x26;height=1040&#x26;id=u31dd2520&#x26;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&#x26;name=IMG_7464.png&#x26;originHeight=2079&#x26;originWidth=960&#x26;originalType=binary%E2%88%B6=1&#x26;rotation=0&#x26;showTitle=false&#x26;size=629986&#x26;status=done&#x26;style=none&#x26;taskId=udecc2e07-f95b-4b09-873f-cab423250bb&#x26;title=&#x26;width=480\" alt=\"IMG_7464.png\"><br /><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/221736/1667550521357-2f23100a-6763-4d9f-a3f7-f581aefa1d97.png#clientId=u3a2c44d1-d614-4&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=1&#x26;crop=1&#x26;from=paste&#x26;height=1040&#x26;id=u88bd6b67&#x26;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&#x26;name=IMG_7466.png&#x26;originHeight=2079&#x26;originWidth=960&#x26;originalType=binary%E2%88%B6=1&#x26;rotation=0&#x26;showTitle=false&#x26;size=764930&#x26;status=done&#x26;style=none&#x26;taskId=u840ff962-4cfc-4fca-a7a0-e94aebf102e&#x26;title=&#x26;width=480\" alt=\"IMG_7466.png\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/221736/1667550534626-53cf8a7f-b8e2-4727-b8b0-69a145e0879b.png#clientId=u3a2c44d1-d614-4&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=1&#x26;crop=1&#x26;from=paste&#x26;height=1040&#x26;id=u5193938e&#x26;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&#x26;name=IMG_7467.png&#x26;originHeight=2079&#x26;originWidth=960&#x26;originalType=binary%E2%88%B6=1&#x26;rotation=0&#x26;showTitle=false&#x26;size=543557&#x26;status=done&#x26;style=none&#x26;taskId=u162d4a94-ac73-451a-b559-64bb6419c21&#x26;title=&#x26;width=480\" alt=\"IMG_7467.png\"></p>\n<p><a name=Cv4KX></a></p>\n<h1>没有个人简介</h1>\n<p>一般真人的关注，可以看到一行个人简介。而机器人则没有。<br /><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/jpeg/221736/1667550614085-36a6d6be-09ae-43a1-b784-a4a32a9c22ba.jpeg#clientId=u3a2c44d1-d614-4&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=1&#x26;crop=1&#x26;from=paste&#x26;height=1040&#x26;id=u724a41ac&#x26;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&#x26;name=IMG_7469.jpeg&#x26;originHeight=2079&#x26;originWidth=960&#x26;originalType=binary%E2%88%B6=1&#x26;rotation=0&#x26;showTitle=false&#x26;size=221804&#x26;status=done&#x26;style=none&#x26;taskId=uc057eaeb-02a7-453f-bbab-16dc53c78e5&#x26;title=&#x26;width=480\" alt=\"IMG_7469.jpeg\"></p>\n<p><a name=eZpL2></a></p>\n<h1>性别全是女</h1>\n<p>这些机器人的性别，都显示是女。哪怕用了男人的名字，但点进去看个人资料，却显示是女性。这一看就是和个人简介一样，没有设置，为空。而知乎的代码逻辑，将性别的缺省值作为女性显示了……</p>\n<p><a name=ExB9H></a></p>\n<h1>没有任何创作</h1>\n<p>全是几分钟前关注了 XXX。</p>\n<p><a name=sv4Wy></a></p>\n<h1>关注者多为 21 人，少数在 22 个</h1>\n<p>有意思的是，他们几乎全部是关注了 21 个人。极个别会关注 22 个。</p>\n<p><a name=tBvbC></a></p>\n<h1>对我的影响</h1>\n<p>本来我的活跃关注者数量几乎是 100%。尽管数量少，但精。现在数据已经被打到不能看了，给人一种低质量账号的感觉。<br /><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/jpeg/221736/1667551068361-fa496d31-1c91-42da-8c33-7fc8d48ff45f.jpeg#clientId=u3a2c44d1-d614-4&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=1&#x26;crop=1&#x26;from=paste&#x26;height=1040&#x26;id=u98798684&#x26;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&#x26;name=IMG_7462.jpeg&#x26;originHeight=2079&#x26;originWidth=960&#x26;originalType=binary%E2%88%B6=1&#x26;rotation=0&#x26;showTitle=false&#x26;size=204393&#x26;status=done&#x26;style=none&#x26;taskId=u76f7a1c1-fd54-4b37-bce4-b873538a451&#x26;title=&#x26;width=480\" alt=\"IMG_7462.jpeg\">\n<a name=mhgsA></a></p>\n<h1>这究竟是机器人进化的魔高一丈，还是知乎的反欺诈中心故意放水？</h1>","pages":[],"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Jeff Tian","description":"A wild full stack developer","palette":"yellow","header":{"title":"Jeff Tian","tagline":"A wild developer","logo_img":"https://images.ctfassets.net/qixg1o8tujmf/7z1ua3nTOC5B7DwwzAki8I/4e1a05f8db770c285a492eeb1eaa398f/imageedit_3_2509022194.png","background_img":"https://images.ctfassets.net/qixg1o8tujmf/7m0jrKYaDBwEvlc5lo8nt6/6d50a5050d9cdc0d4d2047e35feac292/10648733_696750647079056_2800539603462658695_o.jpg","has_nav":true,"nav_links":[{"label":"Home","url":"/","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"About","url":"/about","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"关于","url":"https://ggyy.pa-pa.me/about","style":"link","icon_cl